commit.message: Include botan/build.h which is no longer included from the botan/ffi.h
CI: fix accidentally broken centos-fedora workflow
Relax base64 decoding: allow spaces and tabs between the crc and footer.
FFI: Add function rnp_op_verify_get_format()
Add support for mimemode in literal data packet.
Fix CID 1540660.
Fix CID 1540730, 1540707, 1540701: Uninitialized variables  (UNINIT)
Fix CID 1534296: unchecked return.
CI: bump actions versions to use node.js 20, where applicable.
Fix unallocated objects in PQC-related tests.
CI: Add runners with enabled PQC support.
Update tests to support Botan 3.3: move global_ctx to class member instead of global static function.
CI: add Botan modules list to build with PQC support.
Correctly check for absence of backend features.
Update test for rnp_locate_key() with some edge cases and fix possible issue with hex decoding.
Refactor pgp_key_search_t and related types to C++.
Use rnp::KeyStore::get_signer() to lookup for signer's key.
Update pgp_fingerprint_t with vector constructor and size_valid() method.
Make rnp_key_handle_st C++ and remove unused locator field.
Ignore rarely-hit ElGamal code chunk in coverage report.
CI: Update runner with disabled Brainpool to improve coverage.
Remove unused variable.
Fix GCC warning -Wclass-memaccess
Fix GCC warning -Wstringop-truncation
Fix GCC warning -Wformat-truncation.
fix RNP_EXPERIMENTAL_CRYPTO_PQC -> RNP_EXPERIMENTAL_PQC
add mandatory direct-key signature for v6 certificates
clang format
give salg a defined value when parsing pkesk
fix PQC key combiner fixedInfo
